briefdescription.para: Exceptions that can be thrown from AthContainers.

ref.tooltip: Exception --- Aux data requested from object with no store.
Exception --- Attempt to retrieve nonexistent aux data item.
Exception --- Non-const operation performed on const aux data.
Exception --- Attempt to set aux data store on container that doesn't track indices...
Exception --- Bad use of private store.
Exception --- Type mismatch for aux variable.
Exception --- Attempted to do OP on a BASE base class of COMPLETE; can only be done...
Exception --- Attempted to modify auxiliary data in a locked store.
Exception --- Attempted to insert a unique_ptr to a non-owning container.
